Yes just download and burn onto a cd,(with some img burning software i like img burn) make sure you use quality cd otherwise it might not work, Note that this cd is for BMW, High NAV Systems Non i-drive (MK I, MK II, MK III MK, IV) and only i-drive 7 series that uses NAV001, NAV002, NAV003.
PS. Since BMW is a clone of CarIn and VDO Daytona, this CD might work in your CarIn VDO device
